<hw>Brake</hw> <pr>(br⟦amac⟧k)</pr>, <def><pos>imp.</pos> of
<er>Break</er>.</def> <mark>[Arhaic]</mark>
<rj><au>Tennyson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
